title: Quick Bacon, Crumbly Cheese & Pumpkin Filo Pie with Radish & Mixed Leaf Salad
description: This cosy dinner packs in a veggie-loaded bacon base that's full of flavour, then tops off the whole dish with a light and flakey filo pastry. Be sure to serve it fresh from the oven for an optimally crisp pastry!

